Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:19.50,Default,Nitta,0,0,0,,The whole reason they kept quiet about {*}Miss Ieiri{*Ieiri-san}{\fscx180}â€”{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:23.46,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,...was to prevent me from doing\N something reckless like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:27.38,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,That's probably why the paramedics were late too. {what. i mean it's correct but like, what did she mean by this?} {maybe it's like: that's prolly why the paramedics could afford to be late?} {she's implying that the paramedics took their sweet time just to stall her from running off doing sth reckless, as mentioned in literally the previous line} {right... i'm dumb}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:35.81,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Whatever the case, I can't just leave\N while they're still fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:36.98,Default,Nitta,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:38.85,Default,Nitta,0,0,0,,Kugisaki{**-san}!
Comment: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:01.00,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:31.05,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:43.48,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I should've had Dagon\N leave me a few more humans.\h
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:47.44,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Still, this is plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:51.53,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.45,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:05.71,Cursed,NPC,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.05,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.09,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:07.60,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's avoiding my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:11.36,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must've heard the report from that 7:3 sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.11,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,You're no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:24.83,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm only a double, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:29.04,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can still alter my own shape,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:31.54,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I can't manipulate transfigured humans
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:34.42,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}or interfere with others' souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:41.55,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}So thanks for wearing your nerves down all on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:47.18,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,I already told you, that won't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.19,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:54.57,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I know, but sometimes you just gotta try anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:01.82,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:04.70,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Hairpin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:08.16,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}She jumped down? What is she trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.66,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Here's some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:14.50,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Hairpin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:17.92,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}She used the fallen nails!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.34,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to try this. {...been dying to try this...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.31,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Ever since I heard about your technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:29.06,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I've thought {\i1}this{\i0} would work nicely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:32.14,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Resonance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:43.32,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Kugisaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.29,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:49.75,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:56.13,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Itadori Yuji wasn't my only natural enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:00.46,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:05.60,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I just felt my cursed energy\N explode somewhere else nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:08.81,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Let's see, your cursed energy\N isn't all that strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:12.06,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,and you passed on the chance\N to grab me earlier, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:17.61,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,You're some kinda double who\N can't use its technique, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.61,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.54,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her technique's effects are still lingering!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:40.76,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't get my body to move like it should!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:47.68,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kugisaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.51,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:56.31,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't save anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.40,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wasted everyone's efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:01.65,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:07.91,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}You showed me that I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:09.41,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which is why,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:11.91,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.17,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}kill you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:19.00,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:25.55,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that Resonance is active,\N the attacks should slow down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.93,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,This is where the real battle begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.18,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:36.31,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,I'm outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:38.81,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:40.31,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:44.07,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could just ignore it and head straight to B5,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:48.66,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}but letting that thing run free \Nwould only come back to bite us later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.04,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Underground?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.96,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:02.00,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll exorcise it and head to B5!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:09.68,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}He split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:11.51,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:17.60,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}One of them must contain\N the part of the soul I need to crush!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:22.69,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:25.11,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! He tricked me with cursed energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:35.41,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are two Mahitos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.00,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}He had a double acting separately?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.88,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he planning to merge it back in to heal himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.31,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Itadori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:06.11,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)}Run! Kugisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:14.83,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Hit you dead-on! {nice kill}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:18.16,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.29,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Kugisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:23.83,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:28.38,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't finish off the 7:3 sorcerer with just one touch,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:31.80,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}but what about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.57,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Just die already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:59.33,Default,Fumi's Father,0,0,0,,Not quite there yet, Nobara{**-chan}. {git gud}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:01.79,Default,Fumi's Father,0,0,0,,You gotta crush their chance to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.33,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.34,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:11.34,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used to think everyone in the village was crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:16.30,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that I was the only sane one.
Comment: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:23.06,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:42.16,Default,Fumi's Mother,0,0,0,,You'll be using it until sixth grade. Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.00,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:49.04,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what my mother said,\N but I chose the blue backpack anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:53.47,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}We moved to this village \Naround the time I started elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:57.68,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}My parents were worried about\N the inconveniences of the countryside,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:11:01.27,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I was just sad about \Nsaying goodbye to my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:07.94,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}A total of nineteen students,\N not in one class, but in the entire school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:11.36,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone had either a red or a black backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.49,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I liked both red and black,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:18.53,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}but apparently everyone hated blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.24,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:07.12,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:09.00,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\pos(980,1020)}I like your backpack, Fumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.21,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\pos(980,1020)}Let's trade!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:12.88,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:15.26,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Let's trade!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:17.63,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:20.64,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Hol' up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:23.76,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.77,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I'm the best there is! {something tells me that the point here isn't being number on "in japan" alone}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.69,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Knock it off, Kugisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:35.40,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.74,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Why is it always you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:40.74,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Shuddup, old geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:42.99,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Don't don't bother catchin' up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:48.41,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}My backpack was back with me \Nbefore the day was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:51.21,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I hate all backpacks, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:52.92,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:56.76,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that day, Nobara{**-chan}\N would stop by my house all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:59.26,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}and play video games with my father. {nooooooooooo it was supposed to be Smash Brothers not just gamu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:02.22,Default,Father,0,0,0,,You've gotten better at aerials.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:07.02,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobara{**-chan} hated the other villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.44,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,It's such a small village
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:14.94,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,that it's harder to be strangers than friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:20.86,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought, "Isn't that a good thing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:23.91,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Several years later,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:27.95,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}when the old lady next door brought red rice\N to celebrate my first period,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:32.96,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally understood the creepiness that Nobara{**-chan} was referring to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:37.21,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Fumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:40.97,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I found a secret base!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:49.27,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobara{**-chan} would sometimes say things\N you wouldn't expect from a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:51.85,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}but then also say stuff like this all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:54.86,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,We're living here starting today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:59.03,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thinking back, those were probably things\N she picked up from someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:01.32,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like her mother, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:06.45,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:11.66,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobara{**-chan}'s so-called secret base\N was actually someone's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.42,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:15.96,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,Oh, you really did come by!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:19.80,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,Come on in. It's freezing outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:24.72,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her name was Saori{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:27.89,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}She moved into the village after I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.19,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}We always visited her out of the blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:40.40,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}and she always welcomed us with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:45.41,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that I think about it,\N Saori{**-chan} was always at home, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:49.12,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobara{**-chan} changed after she met Saori{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:52.62,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Oh, yes! Why, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.41,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,You sound like Matsuko{**-san}. {apparently some tv personality?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:57.92,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Fumi, let me practice braiding your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:14:59.88,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:05.05,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her speech grew softer, and it felt like...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:08.01,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}she started to become more refined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:16.02,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were both outsiders, but me and Saori{**-chan}\N couldn't have been more different. {different as in personality-wise or how they are treated by the villagers?} {it's supposed to work both ways i think}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.48,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}A short while after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.44,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saori{**-chan}'s house started to look a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:28.28,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was covered in garbage and graffiti,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:31.03,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}and snow was intentionally piled up in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:35.16,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}It made her nice house start to feel unsettling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.97,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not too long after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.72,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saori{**-chan} moved away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.06,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I saw her off together with Nobara{**-chan},
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:16:01.52,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I can't remember what anyone said\Nor even what the weather was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:09.07,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I remember is Nobara{**-chan}'s messy face \Nwith tears streaming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.58,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}"So even she could cry."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:17.71,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mind was so shocked that nothing else registered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:27.59,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}In June of this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:32.72,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobara{**-chan} was set to go to a high school in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:41.86,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\i1}She fought with her grandma over it,\N and that apparently caused some delays.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:45.94,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Alright! I'm outta here for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:48.99,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Fumi, make sure you find a way out too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:51.99,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:55.54,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}"So she won't cry for me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:17:00.46,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}The awful thought crossed my mind\N and left me unable to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:05.50,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}We never spoke of Saori{**-chan} again after that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.13,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Fumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:13.80,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Next time we meet, it'll be the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:39.16,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:59.14,Default,Coworker,0,0,0,,Saori, why don't you take a breather?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:06.11,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,No can do. The proofs are due today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.11,0:18:08.48,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,Or I guess yesterday at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.28,Default,Coworker,0,0,0,,It's still today until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.63,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,Ugh, I have a pimple!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:31.05,Default,Coworker,0,0,0,,Shibuya's messed up. Could it be terrorists?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:36.60,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,Have you thought about getting married?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:37.55,Default,Coworker,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:39.60,Default,Coworker,0,0,0,,Where'd this come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:44.23,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,Well, I was just thinking\N it wasn't supposed to be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:48.44,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I moved out into the sticks during\N my second year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.61,Default,Senpai,0,0,0,,Parents' job transfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:54.45,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,Not really. It's because my mom is obsessed\N with stuff like organics and spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:56.28,Default,Senpai,0,0,0,,I think I get the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:03.33,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I met these two girls there,\N about seven years younger than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:07.25,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,and this one, Nobara{**-chan}, {\i1}really{\i0} took a liking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:15.18,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I'm an only child, so, to me, \NNobara{**-chan} was just the cutest thing ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:18.26,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I put on my best older sister act\N trying to impress them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.02,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I even made black tea for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:29.48,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,For first graders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:31.78,Default,Senpai,0,0,0,,That's kind of cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:38.87,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,We never did exchange contact info, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:42.45,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I was afraid we would gradually drift apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:48.54,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,She bawled her eyes out when I left the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:51.29,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:55.97,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I wonder if she would be \Ndisappointed to see how I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:02.60,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I hope Nobara{**-chan}'s doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:06.31,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I wonder where she is and what she's up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:17.86,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used to think everyone in the village was crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.32,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was never the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:24.16,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just the crazy ones are the loudest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:27.04,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}They make it seem like they're all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:30.21,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trampling over everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:41.39,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Though, I guess there can be exceptions. {as in those who stand out above the noise}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:05.45,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Sorry, Fumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:12.54,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I couldn't keep our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:22.51,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Itadori, tell everyone for me:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:26.77,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,It wasn't so bad! {what does "it" refer to? life? or all the craziness?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:54.08,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Kugisaki?
Comment: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:55.09,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:25.05,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:28.05,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}When I first stepped off at Tokyo Station,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:32.43,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was a bit grossed out because the air\N smelled like I was standing behind a truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:34.93,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now it doesn't bother me at all, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:37.06,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next time, Right and Wrong, Part 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:39.65,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Maybe life is all about the dirt we pick up.
